latestPosts.caption:
Life felt so normal just a few days ago - Laughing, playing, working, dancing and enjoying simple moments…

In a world where borders can become battlegrounds and peace is often taken for granted, today I pause and reflect on how lucky we are to live happily in the comfort of our homes. How incredibly fortunate we are to have the freedom to move, to dream, to just be. 
All thanks to the countless men and women in uniform who risk everything so we can sleep peacefully at night. Your courage, discipline and sacrifices do not go unnoticed. You are the reason we can celebrate our festivities, dream our dreams and live without fear. Grateful today and everyday for your selfless service 🫡🤍

#gratitude #salutetosoldiers #thankyouforyourservice #freedomisnotfree #peace #life #love
